# =============================================================================
# COMPREHENSIVE PATTERN MATCHING
# =============================================================================
# Block files containing API keys, tokens, or secrets
**/*api-key*
**/*secret*
**/*password*
**/*token*
**/*credential*

# Block common secret file patterns
**/secrets/
**/.secrets/
**/private/
**/.private/
**/confidential/
**/.confidential/

# Block environment files in any subdirectory
**/.env*
**/env.*
**/.env.*

# =============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =============================================================================
# This .gitignore file is designed for maximum security:
#
# 1. ALL environment and secret files are blocked
# 2. Build artifacts and temporary files are blocked
# 3. IDE and editor specific files are blocked
# 4. Operating system files are blocked
# 5. Backup and archive files are blocked
# 6. Any file patterns matching secret keywords are blocked
#
# IMPORTANT: If you need to track a configuration file,
# use the ALLOWLIST section at the bottom and add explicit exceptions.
#
# BEFORE OVERRIDING ANY OF THESE RULES:
# 1. Consult with security team
# 2. Ensure no secrets are included
# 3. Consider using encrypted files instead
# 4. Document the reason for exception

